usoclient.exe is used for CLI Windows Updates in Windows 10+

Available switches are:

RefreshSettings
ResumeUpdate
ScanInstallWait
StartDownload
StartInstall
StartScan

Basic example to trigger a check for updates (Note that there are no slashes and capital letters are important):

usoclient StartScan

To fully automate, combine ScanInstallWait and StartInstall with a reboot via shutdown or psshutdown etc.
